h1. Description

The log mbean management bundle exposes a Log MBean that can be used with any JMX client (for instance JConsole).

The Log MBean allows quite the same actions that can be performed using log:* commands:
  * display()
  * display(logger)
  * get()
  * get(logger)
  * set(level)
  * list(level, logger)

